      "- ${4:forbidden behavior or out-of-scope item}",
      "",
      "## Acceptance criteria",
      "- [ ] ${5:verifiable criterion}",
      "",
      "## Relevant files/context",
      "- ${6:path/to/file or contact}",
      "",
      "## Reasoning effort",
      "- ${7|Balance speed and depth based on the task.,Think carefully and step-by-step before responding; this problem is harder than it looks.,Prioritize responding quickly rather than thinking deeply. When in doubt\\, respond directly.|}",
